Package: dplyover
Title: Functions to apply column transformations based on strings in 'dplyr'
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Tim",
           family = "Tiefenbach",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "mailme@tim-tiefenbach.de",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9443-2434"))
Description: This package extends 'dplyr's functionality by allowing column
    transformations based on character vectors in 'mutate' and 'summarise' calls,
    using a syntax similar to the existing 'across' function.
